{"tid":1595580,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"要求強制要會員自己set自選台","createTime":"2019-09-26T06:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T09:07:20.000Z","uid":431,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"40511a7ecb7981d2273daf1cc6657611ad2dd0f7","tid":1595580,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:30:49.000Z","msg":"原來連仔限制咗時事台喺熱門嘅數量<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593944</a><br />\n<br />\n上邊個post啲人講嘢有文有路正正常常<br />\n但上到熱門嘅非反送中post入面成班熱門狗jer住嚟拉拉拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全阻礙討論點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早講咗個熱門唔係嚟自一個台 cc台自己有自己嘅熱門<br />\n熱門同cc台一樣使鬼要熱門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議逼嗰班撚屌自己set自選台做開app嘅首頁 塞住佢哋把嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545e993bf1a385002a87a5a0fb9f0f5fe27e9bfc","tid":1595580,"uid":227851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"小氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fced69b188e568451c3ac6371295b218a923d79","tid":1595580,"uid":15473,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:36:05.000Z","msg":"開始懷疑你開post 有錢分"},{"pid":"c6e3dc8f751666d4842fd3638376be7f915a34a2","tid":1595580,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fced69b188e568451c3ac6371295b218a923d79","tid":1595580,"uid":15473,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:36:05.000Z","msg":"開始懷疑你開post 有錢分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"直頭個壇我有份添啦<img src=\"/asset